To update to the latest upstream QMK version:
# git checkout master
# git fetch upstream
# git pull upstream master
# git push origin master

Do the standard work in a different branch (i.e. specific for a keymap) 
# git checkout keymap/metsie

If any conflicts occur: 
https://docs.qmk.fm/#/newbs_git_resolving_merge_conflicts
https://docs.qmk.fm/#/newbs_git_resynchronize_a_branch
